01:15.343 --> 01:18.846
* I PUT YOU RIGHT DOWN

01:18.879 --> 01:20.114
* I NEVER REALLY LEAVE

01:20.148 --> 01:23.451
* I JUST SLIP AWAY

01:23.484 --> 01:26.620
* WELL, IT'S NOT MY PURPOSE
